AriaWebPartEnterTemplate.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Screen reader instruction to enter the web part when it's selected. {0} is webpart title such as "Text Web Part"
AriaWebPartEnterTemplate.value: {0}. Press Enter to enter the web part. When inside, use Alt+F10 to go to toolbar, use Alt+P to move focus to the property pane and use Escape to exit the web part.

CanvasZoneAriaGoToToolbar.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Aria label for the keyboard action to navigate to canvas control toolbar
CanvasZoneAriaGoToToolbar.value: Press enter to focus inside the web part. After you are in the web part, press escape to return to the toolbar.

CanvasZoneAriaGoToWebPart.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Aria label for the keyboard action to navigate inside the web part
CanvasZoneAriaGoToWebPart.value: Press enter to go to the web part's toolbar, you can then press escape to return here.

CanvasZoneAriaWebpartName.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]What screen reader reads when the web part with display name {0} is selected e.g. "Image Carousel Web Part"

ConfirmationDialogYes.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Confirming the action prompted by the dialog.

ConfirmationDialogNo.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Dismissing the action prompted by the dialog.

DeleteZoneConfirmationDialogMessage.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]The body text of the delete confirmation dialog asking if the user wants to delete a section which may or may not have web parts
DeleteZoneConfirmationDialogMessage.value: Are you sure you want to delete this section and its web parts?

DeleteConfirmationDialogTitle.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Title of the dialog overlay to delete a web part.

DeleteConfirmationDialogMessage.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]The body text of the delete confirmation dialog asking if the user wants to delete a web part.
DeleteConfirmationDialogMessage.value: Are you sure you want to delete this web part?

TextWebPartPlaceholder.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Default placeholder text for Text Web Part

TextWebPartDisplayName.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Display name for Text Web Part in toolbox

TextWebpartDescription.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Name of control for text input in the webpart toolbox.

ToolbarConfigButtonTitle.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Title for config button in canvas control toolbar

ToolbarDeleteButtonTitle.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Title for delete button in canvas control toolbar

ToolbarNavigationArrowKeys.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Screen reader instruction for using the arrow keys to navigate inside the toolbar.
ToolbarNavigationArrowKeys.value: Use arrow keys to navigate inside the toolbar.

ToolboxAriaLoadingAlert.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Screen reader alert to indicate the spinner is active while fetching web part manifests.
ToolboxAriaLoadingAlert.value: The toolbox is loading web parts.

ToolboxAriaLoadingFinishedAlert.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Screen reader alert to indicate the spinner is finished fetching web part manifests.
ToolboxAriaLoadingFinishedAlert.value: The toolbox finished loading web parts.

ToolboxErrorMessage.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Error message when there was a failure fetching the web part manifests from the server.
ToolboxErrorMessage.value: There was an error fetching the web parts. Not all web parts may be available.

ToolboxGroupNameFeatured.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Group name for Featured Web Part group

ToolboxGroupNameNonFeatured.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Group name for Non Featured Web Part group

ToolboxNavigationArrowKeys.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Screen reader instruction for using the arrow keys to navigate inside the toolbox . {0} is the placeholder for localized count of items in the toolbox from CanvasItems. For example, "3 items"
ToolboxNavigationArrowKeys.value: {0} Use Left or Right to navigate. Use Enter to add the selected web part.

CanvasItems.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas] Accessible count of items in the toolbox. Placeholder{0}: The number of items in the toolbox.
CanvasItems.value: {0} items in the toolbar.||{0} item in the toolbar.||{0} items in the toolbar.

CanvasItemsInterval.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas] "||" are separated intervals for the numbers. These intervals will be used to pick the right localized text for the specific number of elements.

ToolboxSectionHeader.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Header in the Toolbox for section parts.

ToolboxOneColumnPart.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Display name in the Toolbox for a one column part.

ToolboxTwoColumnPart.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Display name in the Toolbox for a two columns part.

ToolboxThreeColumnPart.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Display name in the Toolbox for a three columns part.

ToolboxOneThirdRightColumnPart.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Display name in the Toolbox for a one third right column part.

ToolboxOneThirdLeftColumnPart.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Display name in the Toolbox for a one third left column part.

ToolboxFullWidthColumnPart.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Display name in the Toolbox for a full bleed column part.

SectionPropertyPaneColumnGroupName.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-Canvas]Title of the section property pane column group.
